                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Execute an sql query, so that it results in overflow conditions.&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;EX - SELECT 9223372036854775807 + 1 result =&#160;-9223372036854776000&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

